  "text": "The model can be revised to eliminate this hazard by replacing the self-inhibition of Cdc20 with inhibition of Cdc20 by Cdh1, as shown in Figure 1C , ensuring that Cdh1 transitions to 1 before Cdc20 transitions to 0. This change is supported by Huang, et al. [CITATION_1] , who show that APC-Cdh1 accelerates the degradation of APC-Cdc20 in vivo.",
